1) emerge x11-libs/vte

Though you may need a newer version of vte, or you may not run gentoo so go here to get the vte sources:
ftp://ftp.gnome.org/pub/GNOME/sources/vte/

2) Edit config.h to your specific needs, should be self explanatory.

3) gcc `pkg-config --cflags --libs gtk+-2.0` -lpthread -lvte -otilde tilde.c

4) ./tilde

5) ./tilde -T to move the terminal up and down
